NodeVisitor<ExprNode,JsExpr>
public class TranslateToJsExprVisitor
extends AbstractExprNodeVisitor<JsExpr>

Visitor for translating a Soy expression (in the form of an ExprNode) into an equivalent JS expression.

Important: Do not use outside of Soy code (treat as superpackage-private).
